5- .env


create and .env file in the src of the project.

and add inside:

REACT_APP_API_URL=http://localhost:8000/api

2-go to signup and test it

inside the Layout body add:

{process.env.REACT_APP_API_URL}


3-inside the src create a file called config.js

and inside add:

export const API = process.env.REACT_APP_API_URL

replace this: {process.env.REACT_APP_API_URL} with {API} 
